பொர
வி.பெ. to fight
to contend in warfare
to en gage in battle
போர்செய்ய
2. to compete
to vie with in games of chance
சூதாட
3. to resemble
ஒப்பாக
4. to join
to unite with
to be combined
பொருந்த
5. to come in collision with
தாக்க
6. [fig.]
to quarrel
வாதாட
